Description: Yet Another Home Assistant Client
 yahac is a desktop application that provides a system tray interface
 for Home Assistant. It allows users to monitor sensors and control
 switches directly from their desktop.
 .
 Features:
  * System tray integration
  * Home Assistant API support
  * MQTT connectivity
  * Cross-platform compatibility
